title: Police rushing to incident on Taieri Mouth Rd near Dunedin
text:
Police rushing to incident on Taieri Mouth Rd near Dunedin Last updated 12:34, February 21 2017 FAIRFAX NZ 
15082016 NEWS Photo: MARION VAN DIJK /Fairfax NZ Police car. Generic 
Police are rushing to an incident on Taieri Mouth Rd near Dunedin. 
A police spokeswoman said no further information was available. 
A witness reported police cars "screaming" towards Taieri Beach. 
Are you in the area? newstips@stuff.co.nz 
More soon.
